| N-3 | T-BOTH with whitespace-padded strings | Single-payload agent | Should behave identically to T-BOTH |
| N-5 | Rebuild containers twice | Main session | `ADD COLUMN IF NOT EXISTS` must not error on re-run |

**Round gate:** all three must pass (small stakes).

